<p>Hello <%= @user.first_name %>!</p>

<p>A new <%= @user.type.titleize %> account has been created for you for on the Small Firms Loan Guarantee and Enterprise Finance Guarantee schemes web portal.</p>

<p>To login to your account, <strong>you must first set-up a password</strong> by following this link:</p>

<p><%= link_to 'Set your password', edit_password_url(@user, reset_password_token: @token) %></p>

<p>For security purposes, this link will expire after 7 days. If the link has expired, just go back to the login page and reset your password and you'll receive a new link.</p>

<p><strong>You will not be able to login to your account until you have set your password.</strong></p>

<p>For future logins to your account, your username is <strong><%= @user.username %></strong> and you should use the password you have chosen.</p>

<p>The link to the new web based system is <%= root_url %></p>

<p>If you have difficulty logging into your account, please contact <a href="mailto:efg-support@digital.cabinet-office.gov.uk">efg-support@digital.cabinet-office.gov.uk</a></p>

<p>Regards,</p>
<p>The EFG Team</p>
